      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey my eye is super red and kinda painful. it's also been crusting up a bit in the mornings so it's hard to open. i probably just have really dry eyes from being on my laptop all day for work. do u think i should just get some lubricating eye drops from the pharmacy to see if that helps?",
