      "role": "user",
      "content": "antihistamine drops? i wasnt thinking of those. would those be safe to use even if it's a bit swollen? i really don't want to go to the doctor right now if i can help it, it's just a hassle. i can probably just manage with those for a few days until it settles down, right?",
