      "content": "okay thanks. i think i'll try the antihistamine ones. actually i think i have some old antibiotic drops at home too from a different eye thing last year. would it be okay if i just use those instead of the antihistamine ones to make sure it's actually killing whatever is causing it? i'd rather just get it sorted fast so i can get back to work.",
